:SKRSLUT.
.br
*¤Consider
.in 5mm nobreak
your Dankort and Visa/Dankort cards to be hard cash - and keep them in
a safe place both at home and when you are travelling. For example, never
leave them lying around in the open.
.in 0mm
.br
*¤Learn
.in 5mm nobreak
