3.¤If your Dankort card is lost or stolen
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
If your Dankort or Visa/Dankort card is lost or stolen, report this
immediately. You must do the same if you suspect that someone had
learned your PIN code or that others are using your card or card number
inappropriately.
.br
Contact &BANKNAVN. or Nets immediately on:
.br
.in 15mm
