11¤¤Your responsibility in the event of misuse of your card
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
11.1¤¤In the event that your Visa/Dankort card has been misused by another
person, &BANKNAVN. will cover the loss unless said loss is
covered by Sections 11.2-11.6 below. &BANKNAVN. is required to
prove that the loss is covered by Sections 11.2-11.6.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
11.2¤¤If your Visa/Dankort card has been fraudulently exploited by another
person and, in that connection, the PIN code has been used, you must
cover up to 1,100 Danish kroner of the total amount.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You will not be required to pay more than 1,100 Danish kroner in total if
several of your cards with the same PIN code are misused in connection
with the same incident. However, this is conditional upon you blocking
all cards at the same time.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
11.3¤¤You will be required to cover losses up to 8,000 Danish kroner in
the event that your Visa/Dankort card has been misused by another person
and, in that connection, a PIN code has been used, and that:
.sp 3mm
.of 5mm
*¤you have failed to inform &BANKNAVN. without delay after
realising that the card or your mobile phone with Dankort card on mobile
phone is missing, or that unauthorised
persons had become aware of the associated code,
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤you have disclosed the code to the person who carried out the
unauthorised use, and you did not realise - or could not
reasonably have been expected to realise - that there was a risk
of misuse, or
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤you have facilitated the unauthorised use through grossly irresponsible
behaviour.
card(see clause 10).
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
