liability as stated in Sections 11.5 and 11.6 applies to each card that
has been misused.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
11.7¤¤You are not responsible for losses that occur after &BANKNAVN. has
been informed that the card is to be blocked. Nor will you be held
liable for losses if you have been unable to block your card due to
circumstances at &BANKNAVN..
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
